[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rwanda chosen to host Cecafa Cup

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Rwanda will host the 2015 Council for Eastern and Central Africa Football Association Senior Challenge Cup in November.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Cecafa secretary general Nicholas Musonye confirmed the decision to BBC Sport.
Rwanda will use the event to help prepare for their hosting of 2016 Africa Nations Championship (CHAN).
The CHAN event is a second-tire event for players in local leagues in their respective countries in Africa.
